### ğŸ”’ CI/CD Philosophy

**All deployments go through GitHub Actions** - never local scripts. This ensures:

- Every deploy is tied to a committed SHA (audit trail)
- No "works on my machine" drift
- AWS credentials stay in GitHub Secrets
- Reproducible builds in consistent environment

Deploy commands:

```bash
npm run milestone:deploy -- "title"  # Commit + push + trigger deploy
gh workflow run deploy.yml           # Deploy current main branch
```

